   148	
   149	<!-- ANCHOR:success-criteria -->
   150	## 5. SUCCESS CRITERIA
   151	
   152	- **SC-001**: Every eligible route-gold row exercises the public flag-on compiled front door.
   153	- **SC-002**: Compiled and legacy observations each satisfy the same authored route gold and compare equal on routing fields.
   154	- **SC-003**: Hash/generation metadata differences cannot hide or create a routing mismatch.
   155	- **SC-004**: Drift, missing-manifest legacy, and fresh-manifest breakage are reported as different states using the authoritative shared classifier.
   156	- **SC-005**: D1-D5 scores for an unchanged legacy run remain identical before and after the alignment.
   157	- **SC-006**: The three frozen file hashes are identical before and after implementation and every benchmark run.
   158	<!-- /ANCHOR:success-criteria -->
