.opencode/skills/sk-code/manual-testing-playbook/manual-testing-playbook.md:54:3. The operator captures: which skill won the advisor vote, which surface sk-code detected, which references/assets the AI loaded, which agent (if any) was dispatched, and what the AI's response actually was.
