.opencode/skills/mcp-code-mode/manual-testing-playbook/core-tools/search-tools-relevance.md:38:- Expected signals: result is an array; length <= 5 (the limit); at least one entry's name contains `clickup`.
.opencode/skills/mcp-code-mode/manual-testing-playbook/core-tools/search-tools-relevance.md:48:- Prompt: `Find Code Mode tools for task management and report whether ClickUp results stay within the limit cap.`
