.opencode/skills/cli-external-orchestration/manual-testing-playbook/hub-routing/claude-code-second-opinion.md:26:Strong `cli-claude-code-aliases`/`claude-dispatch` signal (Anthropic CLI, extended thinking) resolves `workflowMode: cli-claude-code`; the hub loads `cli-claude-code/SKILL.md`, not the hub's own thin `SKILL.md` or the sibling packet. The surface router loads `cli-claude-code/references/cli-reference.md` and `cli-claude-code/references/integration-patterns.md` for that second-opinion dispatch.
